  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  elective surgery

          -  combined anesthesia with thoracic epidural anesthesia 8 (Th6-9

          -  Body-mass-index &lt; 30

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Fever, Hypothermia, SIRS

          -  Microangiopathy

          -  Neuropathy

          -  Sensomotoric deficits
      </textblock>
